Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:02.73,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.11,0:00:04.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:06.24,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.57,0:00:07.94,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.76,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.76,0:00:17.49,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,K-Kotomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.42,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't “hello” me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:23.07,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:25.07,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,How do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:29.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,God… And I was having a nice nap…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So I played a lullaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.98,0:00:33.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was about to fall into an eternal sleep from the shock! {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.30,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Okazaki! Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:38.06,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:45.22,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.45,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My name is Ichinose Kotomi. A senior in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:50.15,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My hobby is reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,And her weapon is the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It emits lethal sound waves only 0.2 seconds after she takes position.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:56.47,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The number of people she's felled is countless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.24,0:01:03.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I've never felled people with the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:06.59,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,M-My eardrums…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:08.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Do you see us on the floor right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.33,0:01:11.17,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey! Kotomi! What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.31,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.31,0:01:15.11,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So that was Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.11,0:01:18.48,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kyou-chan, Ryou-chan, Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:20.45,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Hello to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:21.97,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Don't “hello” me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:23.91,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Bonjour?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:26.12,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.74,0:01:31.84,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Bo-n-jour?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.84,0:01:35.46,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Why can't I communicate with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:38.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Please calm down for now, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.29,0:01:41.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She's right. You lose if you get trapped in her pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.74,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.05,0:01:48.20,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:50.48,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Playing the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:54.03,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's the one that was in the music room, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.82,0:01:57.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,They lent it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:01.40,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,They said, “If you like it that much,\Nwould you like to use it for a while?”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.40,0:02:02.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:04.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Allow me to play the next piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:05.75,Default,All,0,0,0,,You don't have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:44.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.52,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It wasn't funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:55.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't make such a sad face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:59.98,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,See, your gags don't have any momentum, and you say them with the wrong timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.95,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's fatal for a comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you understand, go to that corner and take practice swings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.82,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:11.81,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:13.65,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.26,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:16.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What were you guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:17.41,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you don't keep her occupied,\Nshe'll start playing the violin again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:18.91,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:22.93,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Ryou-ch—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're all here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.71,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Nagisa-ch—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.28,0:04:31.96,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,See? You don't have the timing down, so you can't say it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:34.29,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Give it another try, Kotomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:39.68,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:43.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.10,0:04:45.44,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Kyou-chan, was that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.69,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's just say it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.70,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(957.273,411.75)}Episode 11
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:52.70,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}An After School Rhapsody
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I see lots of unique things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.47,0:04:59.39,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's the first time I've opened it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:03.16,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Is the recruiting of new members making any progress?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:08.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Not yet, but I want to get enough members by the time the School Festival comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.56,0:05:12.38,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.52,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think it's a magic wand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:17.39,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Magic wand?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.39,0:05:23.79,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,You say an incantation as you twirl it in the air,\Nand then you transform with flying stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:32.21,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tibi, magnum Innominandum,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:36.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Signa stellarum nigrarum
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:41.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Et bufaniformis Sadoquae sigillum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:32.21,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,To you, the great Not-To-Be-Named,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:36.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,signs of the black stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:41.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and the seal of the toad-shaped Tsathoggua.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:41.00,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: This incantation is from the fictional grimoire, De Vermis Mysteriis, part of the Lovecraft Mythos
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:46.39,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Looks like nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:50.79,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Maybe I didn't enunciate it correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:53.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But you're amazing, Kotomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:58.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to be able to recite lines smoothly like you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.60,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,They're all getting along well, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.60,0:06:03.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should go join the conversation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.95,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You want me to hold that wand and recite strange incantations?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.95,0:06:08.88,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Can you even see me doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:14.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:16.74,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Piraruku Piraruku Gyo Gyo Gyo Gyo Gyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.04,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I love fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.73,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Can I punch you until you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:25.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.94,0:06:34.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The conversation drifted towards saying she's better with the violin than incantations.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.17,0:06:35.99,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you have to play it, play it somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:39.51,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If the reputation of the drama club is tarnished, you'll cause the president trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.51,0:06:41.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:46.33,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I want a lot of people to hear it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:54.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's probably a good thing you feel that way,\Nseeing how you used to hide in the library, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:07:01.20,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Plus, I have to return this violin to the music room eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.82,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So I want to play it as much as possible while I have the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.70,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Let's do something about it, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.38,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Let's see… {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:11.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Okay. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:15.58,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow, on Monday, we'll hold your violin recital. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:17.34,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Recital?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.95,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,We'll gather more people for you on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.95,0:07:23.59,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So you're prohibited from playing the violin here until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.68,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Recital…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.10,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll go practice then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:33.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,May I accompany you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.61,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:37.36,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.13,0:07:40.99,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I'll work out the details for the recital with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.99,0:07:44.41,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Okay, then we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:47.49,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,See you later, Tomoya-kun, Kyou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:51.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Work out what details?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:55.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,I was just splitting you and Kotomi up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.30,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She's always all over you, head-to-toe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:00.13,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So I thought it would be better for her to spend time with other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.81,0:08:02.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.47,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Therefore, {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:06.81,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,we've been left alone. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.16,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What should we do? {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.16,0:08:09.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm tired, so I'm going to sleep. {ep10}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:12.31,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're super rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:15.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please don't screw around with me while I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:24.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You think it was all right to leave them alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.31,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You really do have a tendency to spoil children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:31.08,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Both Ryou and the President are there, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'm worried because it's those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:37.82,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Hey, you said you don't have\Na girl you're dating now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.46,0:08:44.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If there was a girl out there who loved you so much that she couldn't control herself…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:45.13,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,…would you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:46.01,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,…date her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.26,0:08:48.80,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What's this, all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.80,0:08:50.43,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Just answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.43,0:08:53.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Even if I did, I'm a delinquent bum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:55.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The girl would probably get tired of me soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:58.90,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Delinquents can be well-liked in some cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:00.90,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Especially by girls with good grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then Sunohara is well-liked, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.14,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,That's totally impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.03,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Thanks for your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.94,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.51,0:09:25.20,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,How are you all spending this Sunday morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:28.76,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,Today is a beautiful morning throughout the nation,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.71,Default-alt,TV,0,0,0,,and various events are being held at different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:42.02,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I don't think Nagisa is up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I guess I'll bother Sunohara again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:45.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.76,0:09:48.82,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.22,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are you here? It's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:59.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you a ghost living on campus or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.05,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm here as your host.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.05,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't even go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:06.07,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, are you a bully?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.07,0:10:09.54,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I instinctively stopped you since it was so lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:16.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It was a very advanced joke which puns ghost, a hypothetical creature, {Dei- combine for 16.9}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.77,0:10:23.44,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and host, the noun form of “to host”, the act of catering to a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It wasn't advanced at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:27.32,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Maybe in the B range?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:33.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Frankly, it was at an {\i1}absolutely{\i0\fscx60} {\r} low level.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.03,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You really are a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Honorary library attendant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.21,0:10:44.21,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was borrowing the key day after day,\Nand then the librarian gave it to me…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.21,0:10:46.88,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…and made me an honorary library attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.31,0:10:49.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's why you're here even on a Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.59,0:10:55.34,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm usually reading books,\Nbut today, I'm practicing the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:11:00.23,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was told not to use the drama club's room, so I was practicing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:02.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's your bento for the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:08.84,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was thinking that maybe you would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.49,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,So I made enough for two.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.99,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What would you have done if I hadn't come?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.99,0:11:14.75,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:16.87,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,But you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.00,0:11:20.32,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's an apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.67,0:11:25.04,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's my first time making it,\Nso I don't know if turned out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It looks professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:34.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I used sour apple and coated it with an apricot jam smoothed with rum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:36.24,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,This tea, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:39.27,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I used actual tea leaves for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:42.08,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Itadakimashou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:42.94,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Itadakimasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:49.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is this really your first time making this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:52.50,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um… It wasn't good?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:54.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:57.64,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I can't believe that this is your first try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:11:59.81,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I could eat this nonstop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:02.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:07.07,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you unfreeze when I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you a household appliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:11.81,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Um, is it really good?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Really for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.51,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Really for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.51,0:12:16.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.64,0:12:19.50,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm really, really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:28.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:37.56,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Day before yesterday I saw a rabbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.12,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and yesterday a deer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:42.42,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,and today, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:45.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.24,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,More violin practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.73,0:12:55.51,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Since I'm full, time for a little rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.20,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You know, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:03.50,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Only if you don't mind…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Can we…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.62,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Can we…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:07.60,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…with one another…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.30,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…read a book?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.57,0:13:18.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Hey, books aren't very entertaining to read together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:19.84,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You don't think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Then could you read one to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.39,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I like watching you read books,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:31.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,and I like your voice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:34.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh, but no difficult science books.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.12,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Make it a novel or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:37.58,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:46.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,In order to get accepted into a comedian training school, I'm practicing the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:50.52,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I think that plot is too whacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.93,0:13:52.61,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,It's a violin standup comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:54.79,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,What the heck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.79,0:13:58.26,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,When the dango flower blooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.98,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:00.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Dango?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm cooking bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:08.04,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Tonight, the dango will be making love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:13.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Oh no, the dango are…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:19.43,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The reading says that you have schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.43,0:14:22.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How can you tell that from fortune telling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.35,0:14:23.35,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:28.02,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,The way you see things is proof of schizophrenia.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.02,0:14:29.24,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You can't, Ryou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:30.80,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,He's my patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:34.23,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I knew it was about time for you to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:40.07,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,The gas emitted from cooking bread is unhealthy for human physiology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.07,0:14:41.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.52,0:14:45.02,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Again, that must be due to the gas emitted from the baking of bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:48.77,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.28,0:14:50.46,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:54.31,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, you sounded like you were having a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:56.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was having a strange dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:58.52,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,A scary dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Rather, it was a dream that didn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.55,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:07.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.34,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You know, Tomoya-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:12.75,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:17.89,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I was really happy that you came today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I was sleeping practically the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:24.24,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Even so. I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.24,0:15:26.37,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.99,0:15:31.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Ichinose Kotomi, Violin Recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.77,0:15:33.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The one who made this poster is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:35.11,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.11,0:15:38.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes. Kyou-chan asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:44.01,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Honestly, I questioned the Big Dango Family, but it has a good impact, so I said okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:47.20,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I'm sure lots of guests will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.24,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But will it really be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:54.42,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I have a history of putting up\Nrecruitment posters and getting yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.42,0:15:58.69,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll let them know about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:02.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You should pick up some of her shamelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:06.31,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you're too considerate of those around you,\Nyou won't reestablish the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You might be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.81,0:16:12.85,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Now we go invite everyone we know before the end of the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.67,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.67,Note,Oka,0,0,0,,Staff
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.67,0:16:19.40,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,You gave me an invitation, so of course I'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.03,0:16:23.68,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,It's my first violin recital, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.68,0:16:27.00,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I know it's strange to tell you this, being the one who invited you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:31.17,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,but try to get a seat towards the back and be ready to run at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.34,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.39,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,What did {\i1}you{\i0\fscx24.75} {\r} do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.39,0:16:37.23,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I just skipped cleaning duty the day before yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:40.75,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah, I only forgot to bring\Nthe lifestyle guidance handout back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.75,0:16:42.58,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Why does that have to get us into this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.58,0:16:45.53,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,I was threatened for eating lunch early half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:50.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's Kyou. She collected all the criminals for their misdemeanors using her class rep status.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.41,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.86,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's with this crowd?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Is something happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:55.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You came without knowing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.21,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Kyou asked me to come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:00.65,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,She said a real cute chick wants to see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.26,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Man, it's tough being a playboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I see. Godspeed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:08.87,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,When I get to know her well, I'll introduce her to you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.53,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:14.22,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I'll let him dream for a while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.76,0:17:16.84,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're here, too, Misae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:19.49,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,The bunch from the rugby club invited me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.49,0:17:22.07,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I had some time, so I wanted to hear what it's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.10,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:29.86,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Would you be Sagara Misae-san,\Nthe dorm parent of the boys' dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:30.91,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:33.71,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm Sakagami Tomoyo. A junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.04,0:17:36.22,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm familiar with the rumors about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:40.92,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You were a legendary student council president, and you're now working as a dorm parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:42.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Student council president?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.10,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Legendary?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.76,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,You're exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:47.89,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,It was nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.89,0:17:48.68,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:51.41,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,I'm aiming to become\Nthe student council president, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:54.12,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,May I visit you to ask for advice in the near future?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:56.91,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,I can't give you much in the way of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.06,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,If you're okay with that, come anytime you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.06,0:18:00.36,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,Misae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:02.00,Default,Guys,0,0,0,,We've reserved the seat for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:02.98,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Misae-san was a student council president, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.76,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,You have my gratitude, Okazaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.76,0:18:11.07,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me to this recital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.03,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:13.33,San,San,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:14.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.75,0:18:15.58,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.55,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So you came…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.55,0:18:19.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I invited them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:22.80,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We can't stay away after being invited by our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.80,0:18:27.46,San,San,0,0,0,,We couldn't come for the Founders Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:28.84,San,San,0,0,0,,so we wanted to make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:31.76,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you sure? Isn't Kotomi's violin… {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:35.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. She's improved a lot. {ep 10}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:38.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There's Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.92,San,San,0,0,0,,She's a cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.92,0:18:42.24,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Not as cute as our daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.99,0:18:47.09,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,All right, thank you all for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.09,0:18:50.54,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Look, she made me buy these.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.09,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,Me too. For ¥300.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.66,0:18:55.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kyou was even making money off of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.32,0:18:57.92,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So you know, the earplugs are your last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:01.59,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,There will be penalties waiting for the spineless wimps who use them early.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.69,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan, your introduction to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.69,0:19:05.84,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:10.82,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My name is Ichinose Kotomi. A senior in Class A.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:13.29,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,My hobby is reading books.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:15.27,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:17.64,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Well said. Everyone, a round of applause.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What's with that lame clapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.71,0:19:20.94,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Give me more noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.56,0:19:24.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She's a pretty good MC.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:28.69,San,San,0,0,0,,I feel like I've met them somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:31.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They're Kyou-chan and Ryou-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.36,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,We became friends the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.88,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Bring them over one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.88,0:19:36.50,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We'll give them a warm welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.49,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:40.27,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Here's the first piece of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:51.13,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,How do you call this an improvement?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.13,0:19:53.80,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,She was doing better during practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.80,0:19:56.43,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I think… I think she's nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.56,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:02.30,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing,\Ntaking advantage of the situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.44,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.44,0:20:10.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Botan! You came again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.40,0:20:12.78,Default,Mis,0,0,0,,What is this violin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:19.37,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi puhi puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.37,0:20:21.15,Default,Cat,0,0,0,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:21.78,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:28.59,San,San,0,0,0,,Akio-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.59,0:20:31.43,San,San,0,0,0,,I don't think I can last any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:34.63,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae… Hang in there, Sanae.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.29,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:45.99,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Looks like everything made it through in one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.99,0:20:48.57,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Although we had fatalities in the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.57,0:20:53.33,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You played the last song really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.59,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My dad said it was good, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.59,0:20:59.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He said he hasn't seen a breathtaking stage performance like this in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.72,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:07.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Why are we all working so hard for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.56,0:21:12.29,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She has this little kid side to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:16.76,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,It's like, we can't leave her alone,\Nand it's tickling our maternal instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.56,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:23.27,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,I feel that I want to do anything if it's for Kotomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.64,0:21:25.98,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're so merry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.95,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,She's your rival, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.52,0:21:30.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What rival?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.33,0:21:32.53,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Nothing! It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:35.28,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Huh? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:36.32,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:37.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.97,0:21:41.09,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.09,0:21:42.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:46.33,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If you have something you need to say, I'll hear it instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.33,0:21:48.04,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Ah, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:51.46,Default,Man,0,0,0,,I'll come back another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.13,0:21:54.26,Default,Man,0,0,0,,Until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:58.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.53,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He's…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.53,0:22:01.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,…a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.47,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,He's a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.00,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Tomoya-kun, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:48.95,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,If I hadn't met you, I don't think I would have had so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:51.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:55.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa, Kyou, and Fujibayashi just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.39,0:23:56.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.97,0:23:59.86,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,If that's true, I'll be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Kotomi, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.16,0:24:07.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Kotomi-chan?
